article_title: Physician Assistant Demand Rivals That Of Primary Care Doctors

article_metadata.author: Bruce Japsen

og.description: Physician assistants are so in demand to treat the nation’s newly insured patients they are coming close to primary care physicians as the health professional most in need at U.S. hospitals and health systems, according to a new ranking.
